    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though you will find some minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular road use. Inside, the cabin is clean and the upholstery is in great shape with no major tears. Mechanically, the car is very strong; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts precisely. It\u2019s a reliable and attractive vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
