    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. The interior is clean and well-kept, showing only minor signs of regular use consistent with its age. All major systems are functional, and it offers a dependable driving experience for its next owner. This is a solid, honest car that has many miles left to give.",
